metadata.name: MDC REBOOT #1
metadata.description: The MDC:REBOOT is a collection of 1889 premium all-in-one card pass on the Ethereum blockchain brought to you by JESSO CREATIVES. MDC:REBOOT NFT holders will attain the right to receive one Season 1 MELTDOWN:CHILDREN NFT per MDC:REBOOT NFT they hold. Note that this condition is valid only at a certain period of time.
